item.description: I’m William Honaker, and welcome to my blog. I hope you enjoy your stay. I am by no means an expert in any of the fields I currently dabble in, but I am certainly better at nearly all of them than I was 5 years ago. With this blog, I’d like to share a little bit of what I’ve learned and what I am learning, even if it reaches only a handful of people (who will probably be R programmers).
THE ADOBE API 2.0 I’m doing it!
Do you want to learn Japanese? I did, and I learned it. Check the links below for a series on how I learned it.
Series Links to series about useful topics here. Japanese Adobe Analytics
